---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { EMAIL, GITHUB_URL } from '../consts';
---

<Base title="Work with me" description="Freelance: auditable RAG systems, LLM cost control, backend .NET that holds.">
  <h1>Work with me</h1>
  <img class="portrait" src="/portrait.jpg" alt="Serhiy Kucherenko" width="112" height="112" loading="lazy" />
  <p>Three problems I take on:</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Your AI answers need to be auditable</h2>
    <p>RAG that cites the exact page; evals that catch regressions before users do.</p>
    <p class="meta"><a href="https://github.com/KucherenkoSerhiy/payments-rag">proof: payments-rag →</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Your LLM bill needs to stop surprising you</h2>
    <p>Caching, spend tracking, cost per feature before finance asks.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Your .NET backend needs to hold</h2>
    <p>Nine years, most of them in banking infrastructure.</p>
    <p class="meta"><a href="/blog/localhost-trap/">how I debug: 10,137 ms → 27 ms →</a></p>
  </div>

  <p>Write me a paragraph about the problem. If I can't help, I'll say so.</p>
  <p>
    <a href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}>{EMAIL}</a> · <a href={GITHUB_URL}>the code speaks too</a>
  </p>
</Base>

<style>
  .portrait {
    float: right;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
